// Strings for the main page Hello there. Welcome to Diction, a word document app tailored for blind people. Please select any of the following choices: Diction The backgorund of the app Tutorial Document If you would like me to repeat the options. Please say repeat. Tutorial, Document. If you would like me to repeat the options again. Please say repeat.
// Strings For Word Doc If you would like to change the font, say font. If you would like to change the text size, say Size. If you would like to start writing, say Document. If you would like to hear what you have written, say speak. If you would like to go back to the main page say back. Font Font Changed Please select your font Please select you text size Size Changed Document Entered.
